sentences: "นก" สวนยศ; birth name: Krirkkong Suanyos; born June 18, 1983)  is a Thai politician and celebrity.
On May 27, 2012, she was elected to represent Mueang Nan District on the Provincial Administration Organization for Nan Province in Thailand, running as an independent politician.

Suanyot graduated with a science degree from Thammasat University when she was 21, holds a master's degree in political science, and is currently working toward a Ph.D. in social science at Ramkhamhaeng University.
